text: Jaime Bendeck (born 21 November 1996) is a Honduran tennis player. Bendeck has a career high ATP singles ranking of 1580 achieved on 30 April 2018. He also has a career high ATP doubles ranking of 571 achieved on 10 February 2020. Bendeck represents Honduras at the Davis Cup, where he has a W/L record of 10–6.
